text: Ankudinovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Gaynskoye Rural Settlement, Gaynsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 4 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 16 km south-east from Gayny. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gaynsky District
title: Ankudinovo
